Cost Tracking Dashboard Mockup. Four panels: 1) Daily Cost Trend (line chart, budget line at 80%/100%), 2) Cost per Query Distribution (histogram), 3) Model Cost Breakdown (pie: GPT-4o 60%, GPT-4o-mini 30%, Claude 10%), 4) Budget Utilization (gauge: current 67%, warning at 80%, critical at 100%). German labels, dark Grafana theme.